===============================================================
              ENTROPY DESCRIPTORS REPORT (H_LDM / H_Q / H_S)
===============================================================
 Formulas    : H = - sum p_k log2 p_k   [bits]
 H_LDM       : full entropy on lambda_ii (diagonal) + delta_ij (off-diag.)
              H_LDM = H_part + w_loc * H_loc + w_deloc * H_deloc
              normalized u_LDM in [0,100] % between H_min_chem and H_max_ref
 H_Q         : delocalization entropy, weight q_ij = delta_ij / R_ij
 H_S         : delocalization entropy, weight s_ij = delta_ij * R_ij
 Convention  : same as LDM  ->  all pairs i<j inside the domain
               Local domain  : atoms of the detected cycle
               Global domain : heavy atoms (Z > 1) of the molecule
